Dobrodošči u opšti vodič za igranje OpenTTD. Ovde će vam biti pokazano kako da krenete sa igranjem i kako da namestite svoju prvu autobusku i železničku rutu. Za ovo će vam trebati oko 30 minuta. Ako zapnete, stavite vaš pokazivač na odgovarajući taster i posle dve sekunde prikazaće vam se obaveštenje koja je funkcija tog tastera. Na meniju sa desne strane izlistani su detaljni vodiči o posebnim aspektima igre, koje istražite ako želite da naučite više o nekoj specifičnoj funkciji.
==Pokretanje igre==
{{en/Phototable|[[File:en/Manual/Main menu new game.png|Main menu]]|OpenTTD's main menu|center}}
Po pokretanju OpenTTD, biće vam predstavljen glavni meni. 


*Kliknite na dugme '''New Game'''. This will open the World Generation screen, filled with even more dazzling options. Leave these to their defaults for now.
{{en/Phototable|[[File:en/Manual/Worldgenerationdialog.png|World Generation dialog]]|The World Generation dialog. The four images at the top allow you to change the climate. We'll leave all options the way they are for this tutorial.|center}}

*Click the big green '''Generate''' button. The game will now create a new world for you to play in, and the game will start.

==Inside the game==
{{en/Phototable|[[File:en/Manual/Tutorial/Aftergamestart.png|after the start]]|Right after the start of a new game.|right}}
The screen you now see is what you'll be playing all of OpenTTD in. In the middle you can see the green landscape, perhaps with an industry, town or forest here and there. This is the world you'll be taming using the tools of your trade: roads, railways, docks and airports. 

At the top of the screen you'll notice a menu bar. Hover your mouse on a button for two seconds - a tooltip will appear to tell you about what the button does. Some of the buttons have menus under them. You can access the menu options by holding down the left mouse button, moving down the menu and releasing on the option you want.
